Subject: [PATCH] 9078: Decompiler: add and use new BITREV and TZCOUNT PCode
 ops

Decompiler: add new BITREV and TZCOUNT PCode ops

Decompiler: run generateParsers

SoftwareModeling: integrate basic support for BITREV and TZCOUNT ops

AArch64: use BITREV and TZCOUNT to implement rbit and ctz instruction semantics

